---
title: Greek Chicken, Orzo & Feta Salad with Cucumber & Dill
description: This fresh, Greek-inspired salad starts with a bed of tender orzo pasta tossed with cool cucumber, briny feta, and tangy Greek dressing flavor-boosted with herbaceous dill. Top with garlic-oregano seared chicken cutlets for a light, filling meal in just 25 minutes.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6765a7fc40dbba16e1c1cc4b-b43cd934.jpeg
